{"tid":698232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(慎入）野生蛞蝓刺身放題","createTime":"2018-06-11T13:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T14:04:09.000Z","uid":165996,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d120ac5ea0e1094923a02e08e6d867aff84aa264","tid":698232,"uid":165996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:31:38.000Z","msg":"是咁的，同朋友喺銅鑼灣食放題，食食見到張檯紙有隻野，望望下仲識郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同經理講返單野之後佢好順手就捉走咗隻野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話應該喺菜到走出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線下次唔食呢間！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/213003_084871717ae991ac00a52996b935fa8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F213003_084871717ae991ac00a52996b935fa8a.png&h=fbc63d22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次記得食之前要睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5080417dcb602ca6534e4e8eaa9b8e3bae0a77b0","tid":698232,"uid":77536,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蛋白質"},{"pid":"f9b95cd4dc8655c0aff0e371f3c2fda1c8e779d8","tid":698232,"uid":159972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇左都唔開胃"},{"pid":"0df4a64ed0e515aa82dfb6869e817caba301b5af","tid":698232,"uid":57835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"佢捉走佢費事你哋有證據"},{"pid":"3c7d6769759d759254